Back in the day Husqvarna use to "battle it out" with Sako of Finland, and if you are familiar with Sako, you can get an idea of the quality you are dealing with. If you would like to know more, shoot me a message or just do that Google thing. On to this rifle...the metal and bluing is perfect; the bore is fantastic, and the action smooth as butter.
